data.text:
RuPaul's Drag Race fan art illustration Birthday card.

Wish a fabulous Birthday with the Ru Paul "We're all born naked and the rest is drag," created with love at home and professionally printed.

Size: 7x5'' / 18cm x 12.5 cm / A5

- It's blank inside so you can write to the birthday person.

- Includes a brown recycled envelope to help our planet a-men!

Our cards are printed with 100% non-hazardous, toxin-free and completely vegan friendly ink and sustainably sourced paper.
